# Web Application Structure

The main web application is a Next.js app located in [apps/web/](mdc:apps/web).

## Key Files
- [apps/web/app/layout.tsx](mdc:apps/web/app/layout.tsx) - Main layout component
- [apps/web/app/page.tsx](mdc:apps/web/app/page.tsx) - Homepage component
- [apps/web/app/globals.css](mdc:apps/web/app/globals.css) - Global styles
- [apps/web/next.config.ts](mdc:apps/web/next.config.ts) - Next.js configuration

## Development
- Navigate to the web app directory: `cd apps/web`
- Run development server: `bun run dev`
- Build for production: `bun run build`

